                "description": "<p>The maximum number of table names to return, if the parameter is not specified DynamoDB defaults to 100.</p> <p>If the number of global tables DynamoDB finds reaches this limit, it stops the operation and returns the table names collected up to that point, with a table name in the <code>LastEvaluatedGlobalTableName</code> to apply in a subsequent operation to the <code>ExclusiveStartGlobalTableName</code> parameter.</p>"
              }
            ]
          },
          "RegionName": {
            "allOf": [
